CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A26, reads: "Among Physique Winners - Sylvester Burnett (left) won fourth place in physique contest, while Santos Martinez (right) took second place in the 'Mr. Western Pennsylvania' finale. Several hundreds witness the physique show, last Saturday night, at the Boys Club of Pittsburgh, 4412 Butler St.  Martinez represented the Boys Club, while Burnett carried the colors of the York A. C., of Buffalo, N.Y."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of bodybuilder Santos Martinez or Richard Madden posing with flexed muscles, in front of dark curtain, with other bodybuilders on right, for "Mr. Western Pennsylvania" contest at Boys Club of Pittsburgh
